description:
21 Wormwood St UNIT 222, Boston, MA 02210 is a condo home that contains 1,010 sq ft and was built in 1900. It contains 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom. This home last sold for $900,000 in March 2025. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $902,400. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $4,588/mo.
